INTENDED USE / RESPONSIBLE USE NOTICE

This software performs read-only static analysis and reports an application's
resistance to cracking and tampering. It does not patch, bypass, decrypt, or
circumvent any protection. It is intended for:

  * developers assessing and hardening their own applications, and
  * security professionals conducting authorised assessments.

You are responsible for ensuring you have the legal right to analyse any
application you load into this tool. Do not use it to facilitate piracy or to
infringe the rights of others.
